# The mounted home accumulates tool caches (.bun, .npm), pi runtime state
# (auth.json, sessions, installed packages), and the user's own projects.
# hako commits ONLY its shipped opinions; everything else is ignored.

# Ignore everything by default...
*

# ...except this file and the shipped pi opinions.
!.gitignore
!.pi/
.pi/*
!.pi/agent/
.pi/agent/*
!.pi/agent/settings.json
!.pi/agent/AGENTS.md
